title: ACTREC Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for Research Lab Assistant
description: The Advanced Centre for Treatment Research and Education in Cancer (ACTREC) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for Research Lab Assistant Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the M.Sc, M.E/ M.Tech., and B.Sc can grab this chance and apply for the ACTREC Recruitment 2025 .
